%description
The "Network" indicator for Ubuntu Touch and Lomiri.

%package devel
Summary: Development files for %{name}
Requires: %{name}%{?_isa} = %{version}-%{release}

%description devel
The %{name}-devel package contains libraries and header files for
developing applications that use %{name}.

%package doc
Summary: Documentation files for %{name}
BuildArch: noarch

%description doc
The %{name}-doc package contains documentation files for %{name}.

%prep
%autosetup -n lomiri-indicator-network-%commit

%build
%cmake -DENABLE_COVERAGE=OFF -DENABLE_UBUNTU_COMPAT=ON
%cmake_build

%install
%cmake_install
%find_lang %{name}

%files -f %{name}.lang
%doc README.md
%license COPYING COPYING.LGPL
%config %{_sysconfdir}/xdg/autostart/lomiri-indicator-network.desktop
